(1072, 'Members of our team have access to the information you provide us. For example, both Administrators and Shop Managers can access:', '', 'woocommerce', 0),
(1073, 'Order information like what was purchased, when it was purchased and where it should be sent, and', '', 'woocommerce', 0),
